    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty\u2014it\u2019s been super reliable and is still in really solid shape for its next owner. It\u2019s got a lot of heart left and is ready to hit the road for some new adventures. It drives smoothly and has been well-cared for, making it a perfect pick if you're looking for something dependable and fun without breaking the bank. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
