    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only the minor, expected road wear consistent with careful ownership. Inside, the cabin is a testament to pride of ownership; the premium upholstery remains supple with minimal creasing, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the high-fidelity sound system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection, featuring a recently completed oil service, fresh brake pads, and tires with plenty of tread life remaining. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts with precision. Included with the sale are a complete set of service records, two sets of keys, and the original owner\u2019s manual. This is a reliable, attractive vehicle that has many miles of enjoyment left to offer its next owner.",
      "price": 36800.0,
