      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with everything so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with you immediately. It's perfect for anyone looking for a well-loved, dependable car without the brand-new price tag. Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
